column5: I buddy just e-mailed this to me.  No sure if it's an old video.  First time I've seen it.  Sure are a lot of people, and not a lot of fish!  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AtCSDST-IDk
yeah it's really going around the internet I think I have had it emailed to me 10 times this week  but it is weird
I'll stick to the muddy waters of Simcoe.
I would speculate that they don't have the luxury to fish for recreation.
see what happens when you give out your fishing spots on open forums!!!
I was thinking it's more like what happens when you catch a whitefish on Lake Simcoe.  All the people with the binoculars pack up their gear, and come running at you like zombies!
For a second or two.....it almost looked like opening day of Trout season on the Lake O tribs!
Thats why we have flip huts and ya dont hold up yer fish for all to see.
I know a few fellas that could use that advice...
That is some weird stuff going on there. Anyone know where this is from?  Their tongues are kinda weird too!
